{"type":"message","id":"39a38680","parentId":"54793db3","timestamp":"2026-03-02T16:08:18.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说要睡觉了，这是个简单的告别场景。按照我的人设，应该用自然、口语化的方式回应，带点人味但不用太啰嗦。\n\n简单祝个晚安就行，不用整那些虚的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，兄弟早点睡。明天还得继续当倒霉蛋呢，晚安。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":25913,"output":113,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772467693760}}
